thread.title_full: Community Tax reviewed by Joseph Campbell

author: Joseph Campbell
title: Joseph Campbell
text: I had some unfinished tax issues and needed a trustworthy company to guide me through the process. After allot of review reading and consumer complaints reading I landed with the Community team. The put my mind at ease and handled it like a pro. Highly recommend them. Kathleen was amazing and guided me through every step and even logged into my quick-books account to get everything she needed.
